snippet.title: Playtonic Friends Presents: Blossom Tales 2: The Minotaur Prince
snippet.description:
Blossom Tales 2: The Minotaur Prince will be coming to Steam and Nintendo Switch in 2022!

Wishlist the adventure on Steam today: https://bit.ly/BT2Steam

For more information, check out our article: https://bit.ly/BT2Info

Follow Playtonic Friends and Castle Pixel on Twitter to be kept up-to-date with more news: 
Playtonic Friends: https://twitter.com/PTonicFriends 
Castle Pixel: https://twitter.com/castlepixel
